How many do we have all together? Seven. Well, we came on earlier and still have a good crowd.

02:54:12.509 --> 02:54:18.343
So, all 7,000 of you, thank you for being here. We're really appreciative of it.

02:54:18.344 --> 02:54:23.709
We'll be back again tomorrow. Do you like the new time? We tried a little bit earlier.

02:54:23.710 --> 02:54:28.728
Usually, we come on about 9:00, somewhere around there. So, we tried something a little different tonight.

02:54:28.729 --> 02:54:32.750
So, if you like this time frame, let us know. We're trying to do something different.

02:54:32.751 --> 02:54:37.558
I get tired of getting in a rut and doing the same thing over and over again.

02:54:37.559 --> 02:54:44.968
And so, that's what we're doing differently tonight. So to those that are used to coming on at 9:00, you can watch the replay.

02:54:44.969 --> 02:54:50.451
So God bless you all. We close by saying this: We love you. Thank you for your support.

02:54:50.452 --> 02:54:54.198
Thank you for praying for my family. We appreciate every single one of you.

02:54:54.199 --> 02:54:58.495
And we are so excited that you pray with us. And we will see you again.

02:54:58.496 --> 02:55:08.940
Remember, put a smile on your face and a song in your heart. Jesus loves you so much and we love you. God bless you and we'll see you again. Bye-bye.

